phrases.catch: I caught a brown cicada! Now it probably feels blue, cicada.
phrases.blathers: Cicadas are obnoxious insects. And not just brown cicadas, mind you...but all cicadas! They flex ribbed membranes on their torso called tymbals to make a loud snapping sound. So rude! Hoo! Yes, it is only the males who make the noise. Sometimes at a volume that can produce pain at close range! Appallingly inconsiderate, I must say...
